1.0.0
Release Date: No due date
Status: Production-ready milestone planned, awaiting final scheduling.

This version defines the complete scope of all planned modules and agents. 
The architecture of the simulation engine, the AI‑based attack‑path prediction system, integrated dashboards, cloud and hybrid environment support, and the reinforcement‑learning–based decision engine has been designed and prepared for implementation. 
Ethical use guidelines, testing frameworks, and contribution workflows have been outlined, and the platform is now in the planning phase for full development and production readiness.
